<p>明天，就是四六级考试的大日子，刚刚正常返校的小伙伴们有没有觉得很刺激？开学就要面临它！想要英语四六级拿高分，写作是重点，今天小编准备了一些热门话题预测及范文，快看！</p>
<p><strong>锻炼身体的必要性以及如何健康生活</strong></p>
<p>题目要求:the importance of doing exercise and how to keep a healthy lifestyle </p>
<p>开头段: </p>
<p>With the rapid development of economy and society. how to keep a healthy lifestyle has raised public awareness in the past few decades.From my personal perspective, it goes without saying that keeping physically active is a key element to such a lifestyle. </p>
<p>中间段(论述the importance): </p>
<p>The evidence that an increasing number of office workers suffer from different types of illnesses demonstrates that spending most of the day sitting is harmful for our bodies. Besides, exercising more remains as one of the top suggestions from doctors, which proves its significance in keeping us healthy. It is universally acknowledged that only with a healthy body can we accomplish goals and dreams in life. </p>
<p>结尾段(how to keep a healthy lifestyle): </p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
